  <body id="msgFeedSummaryBody" selected="false">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>Per recent decision in the <a href="https://drupal.org/node/586146">core issue queue</a>, Drupal core will use a <a href="http://semver.org/">semantic versioning system</a> (3-digit version numbers, e.g. 8.0.1, 8.2.0, etc.) starting with Drupal 8. This means that significant parts of the Drupal.org infrastructure will need to be adjusted to support the new versioning system.</p></div></div></div>
